  <summary date="2022-07-23T17:27:57Z" status="Introduced in House">IHS Contract Support Cost Amendment Act

This bill allows tribes to receive contract support costs for activities that would otherwise be carried out by the Department of the Interior or the Department of Health and Human Services for direct operation of a program, but for which the costs are not fully covered by the amount of funds required by the Indian Self-Determination and Education Assistance Act of 1975.</summary>
